An example program of using OpenGL with Gtk4. You can see different moving figures, add and delete figures, stop and start moving.

To build:
cmake -S moving_figures -B moving_figures/build -DMAIN_WINDOW_DEFAULT_WIDTH=1000 -DMAIN_WINDOW_DEFAULT_HEIGHT=900 --preset release
cmake --build moving_figures/build

To install:
cmake --install moving_figures/build --prefix moving_figures/install
